OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry and
OL,6,Fbright end to the day with some
OL,7,Fevening sunshine around, and a largely
OL,8,Fclear night to come with a light
OL,9,Fsoutherly wind. Staying very mild
OL,10,Fovernight with some places staying in
OL,11,Fthe mid-teens.
OL,12,
OL,13,CFriday:FA bright start to the day and
OL,14,Fstaying dry throughout. Sunshie may
OL,15,Fturn hazy at times, but temperatures
OL,16,Fcontinue to rise above the May average
OL,17,Fin the strong sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
