OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FVery
OL,6,Fwarm or hot over the Bank Holiday
OL,7,Fweekend with plenty of sunshine and
OL,8,Flight winds. Sunshine may turn hazy at
OL,9,Ftimes with some patchy cloud possible
OL,10,Fbriefly on Saturday.
